# CODEOWNERS — who must review changes.
# Works together with the rulesets (.github/rulesets): enable the
# require_code_owner_review rule in a ruleset to make the owner's approval mandatory.
# Syntax: <path> <@owner...>. The last matching rule wins.

# Default owner for the entire repository
*                       @deidron

# CI/CD infrastructure, scripts, templates, rulesets
/.github/               @deidron

# (Platform DLLs are no longer in-repo — fetched at CI time into the gitignored
#  .platform-libs/, so there is nothing to own here.)

# Example packages (as the team grows you can assign a dedicated owner
# to each package, for example:)
# /IntegrationV2/       @integration-team
# /OmnichannelMessaging/ @messaging-team
